🤖 **Common error handling mistakes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No error handling | Use try-catch |
| Swallowing errors | Show error message |
| No retry | Add retry button |
| No loading state | Add loading state |
| No specific errors | Handle different errors |

